es of gold and a slight freezy look that’s universally complimenting. Build up in thin layers to get the optimum rosy look.\r\n<h5>4. Chanel Reflex</h5>\r\nThis Chanel product is a oh-my-god-so-good baked peach blush with a marbleesque finish. With gold shot spread evenly it doubles up as a great highlighter and gives an impressive glow to your face.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'HOW-TO: DESERT GOLD AND SHIMMERING SMOKY EYES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-desert-gold-and-shimmering-smoky-eyes', '', '', '2017-06-15 19:47:49', '2017-06-15 19:47:49', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/tf/cosmetro-sample/?p=173', 0, 'post', '', 2),
